    "body": {
      "zh-TW": "在每個步驟的頂部都會顯示一個持久的進度條，例如「步驟 X / Y」。必填步驟會被標記，可跳過的步驟則顯示「暫時跳過」連結。",
      "en": "A persistent progress bar, e.g., \"Step X of Y\", is shown at the top of each step. Required steps are marked, and skippable steps show a \"Skip for now\" link."
    }
